itu observations to confirm. More realistic lithospheric mineralogy, volcano\nmechanics or atmospheric photochemistry require even more volcanism.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Nov 2021 22:24:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 18 Jan 2022 11:45:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-19"}
