ontrol operates the battery closer to its charge limits, which may accelerate\ncalendar ageing.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Dec 2021 09:00:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 15 Mar 2022 16:22:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-16"}
