ameters of Al and its spall data. The results are compared with\npublished experimental results in single crystal Al.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Dec 2021 09:31:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 29 Nov 2022 06:18:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-30"}
