 Optimal Transport based approach to guide alignment\nlearning. Experiments on four domain-oriented tasks demonstrate the superiority\nof our framework.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Dec 2021 15:47:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-07"}
